snippet.title: Prominence Poker - The Rooftop Update Trailer
snippet.description:
We’re ready to show our hand: The Rooftop update for Prominence Poker drops Sept. 7, 2022. 

The cards are on the table — new to Prominence Poker this time around includes the new rooftop venue with nine-player tables, solo mode face-off with The Mayor and his Henchmen and much more!

Play Prominence Poker for free today: https://bit.ly/3KyiKTl
